theorem Topology.interior_closure_eq_univ_iff_dense {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} :
    interior (closure (A : Set X)) = (Set.univ : Set X) ↔ Dense (A : Set X) := by
  constructor
  · intro hInt
    -- From the equality we obtain `univ ⊆ closure A`.
    have h_univ_subset : (Set.univ : Set X) ⊆ closure (A : Set X) := by
      simpa [hInt] using
        (interior_subset : interior (closure (A : Set X)) ⊆ closure A)
    -- Combine the obvious inclusion `closure A ⊆ univ` with the above to get equality.
    have h_closure_eq : closure (A : Set X) = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
      apply subset_antisymm
      · exact subset_univ _
      · exact h_univ_subset
    -- Translate the equality of closures into density.
    simpa [Dense] using h_closure_eq
  · intro hDense
    exact Topology.interior_closure_eq_univ_of_dense (A := A) hDense

theorem subset_univ {α : Type*} {s : Set α} : s ⊆ (Set.univ : Set α) := by
  intro x hx
  trivial
